ed with the opposite-spin pairs. We show that the charge current\ndensity is maximized, corresponding to the occurrence of a large amplitude of\nequal-spin triplet pairs, when the exchange interaction of the weak ferromagnet\nis about $0.1E_F.$\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Apr 2018 01:55:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-06"}
