as cooling of the trapped ion quantum platform and to\nstudy the occurrence of atom-ion Feshbach resonances.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Apr 2018 13:12:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-17"}
